  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figure.\u00a0<br>An aircraft is at 9000 feet at position (47\u00b030'N 014\u00b000'E) and flies VFR towards LOXA Aigen Im Ennstal airport to land. What action must be made by the Pilot when approaching LOXA airport?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<p>Contact 118.000 over Trautenfels reporting point.</p>",
    "b": "<p>Fly Inbound TRAUTENFELS maintaing the same altitude.</p>",
    "c": "<p>Contact Wien Information 124.40 for clearance.</p>",
    "d": "<p>Immediately descend to 3000 feet and contact 130.00.</p>"
  },
  "correctOption": "a",
